PrecisRe-appointment of JOHN WIELER, of the City of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a full-time permanent member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE BOARD (Toronto Regional Office) who shall hold office during good behavour for a term of five years beginning September 1, 1991.
